before building need to export followings: 
export __ZRT_HOST=something; export __ZRT_SO=something; export ZVM_PREFIX=$HOME/git/libzrt/libc/install; export ZRT_ROOT=$HOME/git/libzrt/libc/SRC/zrt; 

to run with seccomp try any app in this manner:
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:. 
MANIFEST_PATH=dyn-zrt-main.manifest.temp LD_PRELOAD=libzrt.so ./dyn-zrt-main

